{"tid":1219961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實警察都係比人煽動㗎咋","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T11:59:23.000Z","uid":80760,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5045dab63a8f04ca954ede1cd0b89de5e2233155","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:03:35.000Z","msg":"12號果日 警方個個著曬gear 或者著住件背心 咩住書包遮住警察二字<br />\n<br />\n叫佢地攞委任證出黎又攞唔出 <br />\n<br />\n所以依家極度懷疑有人做假狗 潛入警方內部<br />\n<br />\n煽動警方情緒 導致警民衝突 擾亂社會秩序<br />\n<br />\n為左保護警察安全 抽出內鬼<br />\n<br />\n大家都可以出一分力 係街上徹查警方既委任證同查詢佢地既警員編號 以確保警方同市民既安全 將暴徒繩之於法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a657152d91cadb10ff8a750f0efa48cd8b4a138f","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:03:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ac9cb3cf11c1341f119b09f22c6f4d5c3e93039","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:04:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"580859d0f24c521476e17c98c0d296aa00c3ed01","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"062a58583d7544f5d251ca4cd162a7428ad03845","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04b1711ffb1ed7c07af64dafc66630f2aa9fc729","tid":1219961,"uid":55955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:05:04.000Z","msg":"咪再洗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警察同公安有分別咩"},{"pid":"d4424f4d1a71bb1acfab34dc6e3a5d6ed3f25519","tid":1219961,"uid":80760,"like"